              <p class="feature-card-label" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px;">export_orders</p>
              <p class="feature-card-desc">Historial completo de ventas</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a class="feature-card">
            <IconBox variant="plum" size="md">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
                <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </IconBox>
            <div>
              <p class="feature-card-label" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px;">export_customers</p>
              <p class="feature-card-desc">Lista de clientes con direcciones</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a class="feature-card">
            <IconBox variant="plum" size="md">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="22" y1="12" x2="2" y2="12"/>
                <path d="M5.45 5.11L2 12v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6l-3.45-6.89A2 2 0 0 0 16.76 4H7.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11z"/>
                <line x1="6" y1="16" x2="6.01" y2="16"/>
                <line x1="10" y1="16" x2="10.01" y2="16"/>
              </svg>
            </IconBox>
            <div>
              <p class="feature-card-label" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px;">suggest_alternative_platforms</p>
              <p class="feature-card-desc">Análisis de migración</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- ─── Section 12: Seguridad (white, 3 cols with IconBox) ─────── -->
  <Section background="white" padding="tight" id="seguridad">
    <Container>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <div class="eyebrow-badge" style="margin-inline: auto;" data-animate>
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
          SEGURIDAD
        </div>
        <h2 class="heading-bicolor" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;" data-animate data-animate-delay="100">
          Tu seguridad, <span class="muted">sin compromisos.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-subheading" style="margin-inline: auto; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;">
          Diseñado desde el inicio para ser seguro y transparente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3" style="gap: 32px; margin-top: 48px;">
        <!-- No passwords stored -->
        <div data-animate data-animate-delay="100">
          <IconBox variant="green" size="lg">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </IconBox>
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-ink-blue); margin-top: 16px;">Sin almacenar contraseñas</h3>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-slate-text); line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 8px;">
            Tu password se usa solo para autenticarte y nunca queda en nuestros servidores. Nunca.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Open source -->
        <div data-animate data-animate-delay="200">
          <IconBox variant="plum" size="lg">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/>
              <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/>
            </svg>
          </IconBox>
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-ink-blue); margin-top: 16px;">Código 100% abierto</h3>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-slate-text); line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 8px;">
            Todo el código está en GitHub. Auditado por ti, por Komercia, por la comunidad.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Read-only -->
        <div data-animate data-animate-delay="300">
          <IconBox variant="orange" size="lg">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </IconBox>
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-ink-blue); margin-top: 16px;">Solo lectura</h3>
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-slate-text); line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 8px;">
            Los tokens generan acceso de solo lectura. El MCP no puede modificar nada en tu tienda.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 32px;" data-animate data-animate-delay="400">
        <Button variant="link" href="/security">Lee nuestro modelo de seguridad completo →</Button>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- ─── Section 13: FAQ (fog) ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <Section background="fog" id="faq">
    <Container size="narrow">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <div class="eyebrow-badge" style="margin-inline: auto;" data-animate>
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
          </svg>
          FAQ
        </div>
        <h2 class="heading-bicolor sm" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;" data-animate data-animate-delay="100">
          Preguntas <span class="muted">frecuentes.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 48px;">
        {faqs.map((faq, i) => (
          <details class="faq-item" data-animate style={`transition-delay: ${i * 40}ms`}>
            <summary>
              {faq.q}
              <svg class="chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/>
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-body">{faq.a}</div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- ─── Section 14: Final Action Orange CTA (full-width punch) ── -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-action-orange); padding: 96px 0;">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span
          class="eyebrow-badge"
          style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);"
          data-animate
        >
          EMPIEZA AHORA
        </span>

        <h2
          class="heading-bicolor"
          style="color: var(--color-ghost-white); text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;"
          data-animate
          data-animate-delay="100"
        >
          Conecta tu tienda <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">en 3 minutos.</span>
        </h2>

        <p
          style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(248, 246, 240, 0.85); max-width: 42rem; margin: 16px auto 0;"
          data-animate
          data-animate-delay="200"
        >
          Es gratis. Es oficial. Es seguro. El conector MCP de Komercia para Claude.ai.
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap justify-center"
          style="gap: 16px; margin-top: 32px;"
          data-animate
          data-animate-delay="300"
        >
          <a
            href="/sign-in"
            style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--color-ghost-white); color: var(--color-action-orange); border: 1px solid var(--color-ghost-white); border-radius: 8px; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; padding: 14px 24px; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: var(--shadow-callout);"
          >
            Obtener mi token gratis
          </a>
          <a
            href="/uso"
            style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: transparent; color: var(--color-ghost-white); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); border-radius: 8px; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; padding: 14px 24px; text-decoration: none;"
          >
            Ver guía de instalación →
          </a>
        </div>

        <p
          style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(248, 246, 240, 0.7); margin-top: 32px;"
          data-animate
          data-animate-delay="400"
        >
          Sin tarjeta · Sin compromiso · Open source
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Section 15: Footer ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <Footer />

  <!-- Scroll animation observer (must render once) -->
  <ScrollAnimate />
</Base>
